dct_title_s: Town plan of St. Louis. G.S.G.S. 4353.
dct_description_sm: Map shows relevant buildings, and railways. Includes location map. South Sahara grid. "Reprint November 1942." "8/42/G.S.G.S." This is a map of the city of St. Louis, Senegal, shown at a 1:5,000 scale. The map was created for use by War and Navy Department agencies during World War II.
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1942.
